{"type":"message","id":"d1f2e45c","parentId":"02897df3","timestamp":"2026-04-12T11:19:58.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to update the 5p Progress Report cron job so it only sends a report if there are changes (not just a generic \"everything healthy\" message). Currently the prompt says \"Only report if any agent status = failed or blocked. Otherwise send HEARTBEAT_OK.\" but it seems like it's still sending messages every time.\n\nThe user wants it to send a message to the group only when there are actual changes or issues. I need to update the cron job prompt to make it smarter about detecting changes vs. no changes.\n\nLet me update both \"5p Progress Report\" jobs (for DTLX group and the main group) to:\n1. Only send to group if there are changes/failures\n\n\n2. If everything is stable with no changes from the last report, stay silent\n\nI'll revise the prompts for both cron jobs now.","thinkingSignature":"bd83aa1d4e5a2e3d86edb13ec61d885400e9f75fa07cc300f432aa8142f727c5"},{"type":"text","text":"Cập nhật cả 2 cron 5p để chỉ thông báo khi có thay đổi:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wzgxeo6mbyab_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the OpenClaw 34-agent ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5212380728:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.","timeoutSeconds":120}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wzgxeo6mbyab_2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX project ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5168104492:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.","timeoutSeconds":120}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":6127,"output":822,"cacheRead":17535,"cacheWrite":245,"totalTokens":24729,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775992780497,"responseId":"062ab2cd7d63209f7e2522c378450e90"}}
