017` (SHARED với DTLX)\n- **ERD**: Confluence page `23494657` (v35) — 20+ entities\n\n## Agents\n- Use prefix `ahv-dtlx:` for all spawned subagents\n\n## MCP Servers\n- Confluence: Use spaceKey=OTLXPA1 for DTLX docs\n- GitLab: Use ahv-dtlx repos\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776000283909}}
