elegram\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/0d74c438-5460-4bbd-824a-3bdd04655170.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5212380728\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775984447881,\n      \"sessionId\": \"cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 79494,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1775984431083,\n      \"endedAt\": 1775984447212,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 16129,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:senior-backend:subagent:31b6b412-927a-481a-b157-d89c2dd3a187\",\n        \"agent:code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd-07f8-4a08-a4d6-823d773bfe5b\",\n        \"agent:security-reviewer:subagent:6739034d-567f-4c51-8557-f54f81ff565a\",\n        \"agent:database-reviewer:subagent:51a096dc-1f97-4452-938a-8b629dc4e57e\",\n        \"agent:performance-optimizer:subagent:57b179b5-c044-4440-ac46-e970badda4d1\",\n        \"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:fd28add5-35bd-45b1-8ac5-93bd476867bc\"\n      ],\n      \"thinkingLevel\": \"medium\",\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:-5212380728\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"tóm tắt báo cáo tiến độ của frontend\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1775984431082,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"d73ab950\",\n            \"seq\": 348\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Khương hỏi tóm tắt báo cáo frontend. Mình đã viết frontend.md rồi, đọc lại và tóm tắt.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**📋 BÁO CÁO FRONTEND — AHV Works**\\n**Điểm: 6/10**\\n\\n---\\n\\n✅ **Đã làm tốt:**\\n- React.lazy code splitting cho tất cả pages\\n- Route guards (ProtectRouter, GuardRoute, PublicRoute)\\n- Redux Toolkit Query với token injection\\n- 18 modules đầy đủ theo spec\\n- Socket.IO real-time notification\\n- Theme support (dark mode foundation)\\n\\n---\\n\\n🔴 **3 lỗi P0 cần fix ngay:**\\n\\n1. **Thiếu Axios error interceptor** — API trả 401 (hết phiên) không tự logout, 500 không hiện toast lỗi. Fix: thêm interceptor xử lý 401→clear token→redirect login.\\n\\n2. **Thiếu React Error Boundary** — nếu lazy-loaded page lỗi → crash cả app. Fix: wrap routes trong `<ErrorBoundary>`.\\n\\n3. **Ant Design full import** — import toàn bộ thư viện (400+ components) dù chỉ dùng ~20. Fix: tree-shaking chỉ import components thực sự dùng.\\n\\n---\\n\\n🟠 **P1 cần làm tiếp:**\\n\\n- Socket.IO reconnection không xử lý → mất kết nối không tự reconnect\\n- Dark mode có slice nhưng chưa implement\\n- Không có form validation chuẩn (nên dùng React Hook Form + Zod)\\n- Không có request cancellation → request cũ vẫn chạy khi user điều hướng đi\\n\\n---\\n\\n⚠️ **Modules chưa xây (so với Confluence):**\\n\\n| Module | Trạng thái |\\n|---|---|\\n| Chat (1-on-1 + group) | ❌ Chưa xây |\\n| Bảng xếp hạng | ❌ Chưa xây |\\n| Social Recognition feed | ⚠️ Niko cơ bản có, feed khen nhau chưa |\\n| Đánh giá hiệu suất | ❌ Chưa xây |\\n| Đào tạo | ❌ Chưa xây |\\n| Tuyển dụng | ❌ Chưa xây |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Thứ tự ưu tiên fix:**\\n```\\nTuần 1: Error interceptor → Error Boundary → Ant tree-shaking\\nTuần 2: Socket reconnection → Dark mode → Form validation\\nTuần 3+: Xây modules mới (Chat → Leaderboard → Social feed)\\n```\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\nidation\\n   - Uses encrypted data for FE attendance\\n\\n4. **Checkins module:**\\n   - Good separation between Schedule and Abnormal checkin\\n   - validateCreatorInParticipants is a private method\\n   - Good validation of time constraints\\n   - Overall clean architecture\\n\\n5. **OKRs module:**\\n   - Extremely complex aggregation pipeline in getOKRByFilter - lots of nested logic\\n   - No DRY violations detected\\n   - Good RBAC\\n\\n6. **Leave Requests module:**\\n   - 656 lines in leaveRequests.service.ts - VERY LARGE\\n   - Two-level approval workflow (Manager + HR)\\n   - Good leave balance management\\n   - Good notification system\\n   - Some DRY issues: repeated employee lookup, approval logic patterns\\n\\n7. **Auth module:**\\n   - Good token management (access + refresh)\\n   - Cookie-based refresh token\\n   - Solid implementation overall\\n\\n8. **Roles/Permissions module:**\\n   - Proper use of transactions for consistency\\n   - Redis caching for permissions with cache-busting on updates\\n   - Service instantiates itself with PermissionService.callingPermissionMaps preventing race conditions\\n\\n9. **Niko modules:**\\n   - Emotion: Good service\\n\\n, well-structured\\n   - Orders: Uses transactions properly for complex operations\\n   - Wallets: Good balance tracking\\n   - Criteria: Has try-catch with generic error rethrow - not ideal\\n   - Gifts: Good but has hardcoded 'PENDING' string (magic number)\\n   - Cart: Clean service\\n\\n**FE (React/TypeScript/RTK Query):**\\n\\n1. **API files:**\\n   - Good use of RTK Query with providesTags/invalidatesTags\\n   - Some use of `any` types (attendanceApi, okrApi, leaveApi)\\n   - Proper use of overrideExisting\\n\\n2. **AccountPage.tsx:**\\n   - 413 lines - reasonable size\\n   - Good separation of concerns with multiple forms\\n   - Clean TypeScript usage\\n   - No loading states, error handling, or prop drilling issues\\n\\n3. **EmployeePage.tsx:**\\n   - 311 lines - reasonable size\\n   - Clean patterns with hooks like usePermission, AccessControl\\n   - Good use of memoization\\n\\n4. **NikoPage.tsx:**\\n   - 779 lines - VERY LARGE, should be split into sub-components\\n   - Hardcoded emotion data in component (should be from API)\\n   - EMOTION_MAP created in render body\\n\\nNow I'm identifying the critical issues. The attendance module has massive code duplication across multiple files, the leaveRequests service is oversized at 656 lines, and there are hardcoded magic strings scattered throughout. The NikoPage component at 779 lines needs refactoring into smaller pieces. Beyond that, I'm seeing `any` types leaking across the FE API files, missing JSDoc comments in most places, and inconsistent error handling with empty catch blocks in some niko services. There's also mixed language usage between Vietnamese and English that should be standardized, and some files have unnecessary complexity that could be simplified.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Now I have enough data to write the comprehensive code quality report. Let me create it:\\n\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_4mi0q9it66m6_1\",\n              \"name\": \"exec\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"command\": \"mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews\"\n              }\n     