 QLHV — 2026-04-12\n\n---\n\n### 📦 QLHV (Quản lý Học vụ)\n\n| Thành phần | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| **BE** | `feat/notification-migration` 🟡 đang dev |\n| **FE** | `feat/database-master` 🟡 đang dev |\n| **Group** | `-5168104492` — session running |\n| **MCP** | ✅ Confluence ✅ GitLab |\n\n**Commit gần đây (BE):**\n```\n6dac82f docs(openspec): Phase 3 migration verification results\nd8f3dc5 docs(openspec): notification migration execution record\n7ad683a fix: notification migration dry-run read-only\nca6c6fe fix(dashboard): notification stats from 4-collection model\n```\n\n**Commit gần đây (FE):**\n```\nebac17c fix: move ViDateInput import out of function params\n25b1a50 feat: responsive desktop/tablet/mobile R3\nea15786 feat: migrate all date fields to ViDateInput\n0482434 fix: 'Nộp HS' → 'Đã nộp HS' in status badge\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📦 DTLX (Đào tạo Lái xe)\n\n| Thành phần | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| **BE** | `ahv-dtlx-backend` ✅ hoạt động |\n| **FE** | Local repo chưa clone |\n| **GitLab** | ahv-dtlx/* (81078323, 81078350...) |\n| **Cron** | 5p progress ✅ đang chạy |\n\n**Commit gần đây (DTLX BE):**\n```\n47d53ae chore: course student repository!\n4a570ad chore: remove folder openspec\n27f375b chore: implement prettier!\n09a132e perf(course): search queries + schema index\n41b070c perf(courseAgent): search queries + database index\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Vấn đề cần lưu ý\n\n1. **QLHV FE `feat/database-master`** — đang trên branch khác với BE (`feat/notification-migration`). Cần sync khi merge.\n2. **DTLX FE** — chưa có local repo, chỉ clone được từ GitLab.\n3. **`code-reviewer` failed** trong ahv-works review cycle (từ ~11:00 UTC) — chưa re-run.\n\n---\n\nPipeline: 🟡 DEGRADED | Active: 4 sessions | Cron: ✅"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":186,"output":800,"totalTokens":40423,"cacheRead":39141,"cacheWrite":296,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776000493860,"responseId":"062ad0ee0fd7