{"type":"message","id":"14162a43","parentId":"870d9543","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:53:58.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me compile the server status report.\n\nKey findings:\n1. Gateway is running on port 18789 ✅\n2. Memory: 2.7GB/3.8GB used (71%), 953MB available\n3. Disk: 16GB/34GB used (45%)\n4. Load average: 2.05 (high - server is under some load)\n5. Uptime: 10 days 18 hours\n6. MCP servers running: stitch-key, gitlab, confluence (many instances)\n7. Docker: 1 container (openclaw-sbx-agent-researcher) running\n\n\n8. The gateway crashed around 02:51 and auto-restarted, which explains the high load average of 12.17 over 5 minutes as multiple MCP server instances came back online","thinkingSignature":"6f808eb5325891569e78f9b8508b22c4e956f6ffc9a5fac73652d7b897ce476e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🖥️ Server Status Report — 02:14 UTC 13 Apr\n\n---\n\n### ⚙️ System\n\n```\nOS:       Linux 5.15.0-143-generic (Ubuntu)\nUptime:   10 days 18h ✅\nLoad:     2.05 / 12.17 / 20.28 ⚠️ (cao — có nhiều process khởi động lại gần đây)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 💾 Resources\n\n| Resource | Usage | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| **RAM** | 2.7GB / 3.8GB (71%) | 🟡 Khá cao |\n| **Disk** | 16GB / 34GB (45%) | 🟢 OK |\n| **Swap** | 0B | ⚠️ Không có swap |\n\n---\n\n### 🔌 Services\n\n| Service | Port | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| **OpenClaw Gateway** | `127.0.0.1:18789` | ✅ Running |\n| **MCP Stitch** | (nhiều instances) | ✅ Running |\n| **MCP GitLab** | (nhiều instances) | ✅ Running |\n| **MCP Confluence** | (nhiều instances) | ✅ Running |\n| **Docker container** | researcher agent | ✅ Up 4 days |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Cảnh báo\n\n```\n1. Load cao (20.28) — gateway/processes vừa restart gần đây\n2. RAM 71% — còn ~1GB available nhưng không có swap\n3. Gateway port 18789 đang listen → đang hoạt động\n4. Nhiều MCP server instances → bình thường sau restart\n```\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Kết luận\n\n```\nServer:  🟡 ĐANG PHỤC HỒI (gateway auto-res