cosystem fully deployed\\n• All agent configs, SKILL_GATES, DEV_GATE wired up\\n• Ecosystem backup archived (`ecosystem-backup-2026-04-11/`)\\n• QLHV backend: 4 commits — performance hardening, mobile sidebar, startup fix\\n\\n✅ **Operations Stable**\\n• Daily Briefing cron (5AM UTC+7) — Active ✅\\n• 5-Minute Progress cron — Active ✅\\n• Telegram token issues — Resolved ✅\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🎯 **TODAY — SUNDAY APRIL 12**\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🔴 **Active**\\n1. **Stitch MCP Wrapper Testing** — Verify async polling after gateway restart stabilizes\\n2. **Stitch `stitch-connect` Skill Update** — Migrate from OAuth to MCP wrapper\\n3. **AHV Works: HRM & Landing Page** — Feature review pending\\n\\n⚡ **Ready to Spawn**\\n• `senior-frontend` — UI tasks queued\\n• `senior-devops` — Infrastructure checks\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n⚠️ **BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🟡 **Watch:** Stitch MCP wrapper test pending gateway stability confirmation\\n🟢 No hard blockers\\n🟢 No security incidents\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🌐 **PIPELINE STATUS: HEALTHY**\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\nAgents Online: 34 | Active Cron: 2 | Sessions: Clean ✅\\n\\n— *Orbis 🌐*\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 161,\n            \"output\": 402,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35664,\n            \"cacheRead\": 17766,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 17335,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776031328584,\n          \"responseId\": \"062b49618ba3e98360105a7881f89c7c\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"34ae6384\",\n            \"seq\": 14\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8\",\