  \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 5,\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n    \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n  },\n  \"description\": \"5-minute change detection for AHV Works group -5212380728. Only reports when sessions change/fail.\"\n}"}],"details":{"id":"ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","agentId":"master-orchestrator","sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","name":"5p Progress Report — AHV Works","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1775975347574,"updatedAtMs":1776054742076,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":300000,"anchorMs":1775975347574},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5212380728:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"-5212380728"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1776058066020,"lastRunAtMs":1776054345910,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":120110,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":5,"lastErrorReason":"timeout","lastError":"cron: job execution timed out"},"description":"5-minute change detection for AHV Works group -52123807