nd is now **active** — was absent in last baseline\nSystem: • Active sessions: 2 (up from 1)\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **HEALTHY**\nSystem: • Active sessions: 2\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: none\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 13th, 2026 - 12:34 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-13 00:34 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776041094262,"__openclaw":{"id":"87ec9bac","seq":81}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776041094469,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"b804c6f1","seq":82}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776031202690,"sessionId":"b8428c5a-6da6-4dbe-9615-52a4570a78a5","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":35262,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/b8428c5a-6da6-4dbe-9615-52a4570a78a5.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the group session is `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728` and its session key is `cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6`. The last activity was a heartbeat at 21:55 UTC. L