{"type":"compaction","id":"910a4144","parentId":"8b53ab59","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:57:50.346Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Configure 5-minute cron jobs to **only send reports when changes occur**, not on every cycle\n- Keep system documentation accurate (group IDs, agent assignments, cron configs)\n- Recover from gateway restart causing cron timeout errors\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Cron jobs must be silent when no changes detected — no HEARTBEAT_OK messages\n- Only report to Telegram groups when sessions change, agents fail, or blockers appear\n- Master-orchestrator manages both AHV DTLX + QLHV (shared DB) and AHV Works projects\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Updated both 5p cron jobs to **change-detection mode**: compare against `memory/heartbeat-state.json`, stay silent if stable\n- [x] Fixed group ID for DTLX in `MEMORY.md`: `-5168104492` (confirmed via GetIDsBot; DTLX and QLHV share this group)\n- [x] Renamed cron `ed2d0b5d` → **\"5p Progress Report — AHV Works\"**, targets `-5212380728`\n- [x] Renamed cron `6f3323ef` → **\"5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX\"**, targets `-5168104492`\n- [x] Created `memory/heartbeat-state.json` for state comparison tracking\n- [x] Updated `HEARTBEAT.md` to reflect new silent-when-stable logic\n- [x] Increased cron timeout from 120s → **300s** to prevent timeout after gateway restarts\n- [x] Verified 34/34 agent workspaces exist in `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/`\n- [x] Both cron jobs recovered: manual run at 04:34 UTC succeeded, delivered to group `-5168104492`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Clarifying DTLX ecosystem group structure: `-5163901258` (session `g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem`, active with subagents) vs `-5168104492` (cron target, labeled \"QLHV ecosystem\")\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Change detection beats heartbeat**: Cron now uses `memory/heartbeat-state.json` to diff current vs last known state. Only sends to group when something actually changed.\n- **5 consecutive cron timeouts** were caused by gateway restart (~04:22 UTC) making isolated session cold-start exceed 120s. Fixed by increasing timeout to 300s.\n- **Server RAM upgraded**: 3.8GB → 7.8GB after restart.\n- **19 agents still on weaker `AHV-Holding-TroLy` model** (code-reviewer, senior-backend, senior-frontend, etc.) — flagged for potential upgrade but not yet acted on.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Confirm whether group `-5163901258` (DTLX ecosystem session with active subagents) needs its own cron or is managed differently\n2. Monitor cron jobs to confirm they stay stable after timeout fix\n3. Decide whether to upgrade 19 TroLy-model agents to `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n4. Consider cleaning up stale sessions (old QLHV group, failed subagent sessions)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Cron job IDs**: DTLX = `6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31` | Works = `ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7`\n- **State file**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json`\n- **HEARTBEAT.md path**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- **MEMORY.md path**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md`\n- **Gateway**: `http://127.0.0.1:18789/` (loopback only)\n- **Failed subagents still in queue**: `code-reviewer`, `prompt-optimizer:subagent`, multiple QLHV backend/frontend subagents\n- **Active DTLX subagents**: `senior-backend:f42cdd0e`, `senior-frontend:cf1f74df` — settings page rebuild + FE refactoring in progress on group `-5163901258`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nKhương Nịnh asks why the master orchestrator for group -5163901258 isn't responding - they haven't seen any feedback.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant checked sessions list and found 22 sessions\n- Discovered a session for group -5168104492 (note: possibly different from the requested -5163901258)\n- Found an April 12 session still running with active subagents handling a settings page rebuild and FE refactoring\n- Mentioned DTLX cron was working again after timeout fix (increased to 300s)\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe retained suffix shows the master orchestrator providing updates about: the DTLX cron job successfully delivering to group -5168104492 (runs at 04:34 and 04:32 UTC with status: ok), clarification that the cron IS delivering to that group but Lead may be asking about the master not responding to incoming messages, and discussion of multiple active sessions for the group.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/dtlx-context.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"bfdb2b0f","tokensBefore":129417,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/dtlx-context.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"]},"fromHook":false}
{"type":"message","id":"566c962d","parentId":"910a4144","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:57:54.408Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1887\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 04:54 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nbạn cũng cần phải gửi báo cáo định kỳ cho tôi thông tin là có những agent master nào đang chạy tình trạng khoẻ không, đang làm task gì"}],"timestamp":1776056274285}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7217eea","parentId":"566c962d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:08.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to send periodic reports about what master agents are running and their health/status. Looking at the sessions_list output, I can see the cron \"Agent Status to Lead\" (e7885813) was created and ran, but it timed out on sessions_send. Let me check if the report was actually delivered to Lead.\n\nLooking at the sessions_list output, I can see:\n1. The cron session `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e` is still running (status: running)\n2. Its most recent message shows it tried `sessions_send` with timeout 60s and got a timeout, then retried\n\n\n3. The cron ran around 10:55 UTC based on the session timestamps\n\nThe cron session was still in progress when I checked it, so the timeout occurred because sessions_send was waiting for a response from the main session. The cron had compiled a report with 4 active sessions and attempted to send it but hit the 60-second limit.\n\nLooking at the message history, the cron tried twice to deliver the report to the direct session—one attempt timed out and another seems to have started. Rather than waiting for the cron to finish, I should just compile the current status directly and send it to Lead myself right now.","thinkingSignature":"7011710bf5dc4099ae0b7a6ea1c2eff85ac3808cf98a3d87ef13504cd607b0b8"},{"type":"text","text":"Tôi thấy cron `e7885813` đang chạy nhưng bị timeout khi gửi. Để tôi gửi trực tiếp cho Lead luôn:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o0wxoolmmgmn_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 04:55 UTC 13 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 4\n• QLHV group (-5163901258): 🟡 running — yarn build verification — ~2h 47m\n• DTLX cron (6f3323ef): 🟢 running — 5p Progress Report — ~75m\n• QLHV cron (ed2d0b5d): 🟢 running — 5p Progress Report — ~28m\n• Orbis direct (6053576134): 🟢 running — responding to Lead\n\nPipeline: ⚠️ DEGRADED\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Blockers: ⚠️ 2 QLHV subagents failed earlier (senior-backend + senior-frontend)\n\nCron mới \"Agent Status to Lead\" (10p 1 lần) đã tạo xong. Chờ kết quả.","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":11720,"output":588,"cacheRead":18043,"cacheWrite":4134,"totalTokens":34485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056274409,"responseId":"062baad382055cebd82beb7cc8519cc8"}}
