{"type":"message","id":"4e824666","parentId":"60c78c67","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:52.442Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions_send is timing out because the direct session (me) is the one sending to myself. This creates a deadlock. The cron session is trying to send to my session, but I'm currently handling this message, so the session can't receive the send.\n\nThe issue is that `sessions_send` to my own session causes a timeout because I'm currently busy handling an incoming message. I should just reply here directly to Lead instead of trying to send to myself.\n\nLet me just reply to Lead in this session.","thinkingSignature":"4c2967e04eb87936f7ded89ef78c69983326b8c791f179755248cbd16edba6c6"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Đã hiểu Lead! 🟢\n\nTóm tắt cho Lead ngay đây:\n\n---\n\n🌐 **Orbis — Agent Status | 04:55 UTC 13 Apr**\n\n**Active sessions:** 4\n- **QLHV group** (`-5163901258`): 🟡 running — `yarn build` verification — ~2h 47m\n- **DTLX cron** (6f3323ef): 🟢 running — 5p Progress Report — ~75m\n- **QLHV cron** (ed2d0b5d): 🟢 running — 5p Progress Report — ~28m\n- **Orbis direct** (6053576134): 🟢 running — đang trả lời Lead\n\n**Pipeline:** ⚠️ DEGRADED\n- MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n- Blockers: ⚠️ 2 QLHV subagents failed (senior-backend + senior-frontend) — từ session trước\n\n---\n\n**Cron mới đã tạo:**\n- `e7885813` — **\"Agent Status to Lead\"** — mỗi **10 phút** gửi cho Lead\n- Nội dung: session nào đang chạy, đang làm gì, bao lâu rồi\n- Gửi **trực tiếp** vào chat Lead\n\nĐây là báo cáo định kỳ đầu tiên. Từ giờ Lead sẽ nhận được mỗi 10 phút."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":180,"output":468,"cacheRead":22012,"cacheWrite":12368,"totalTokens":35028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056321696,"responseId":"062bab038c413278603122fcf55f8986"}}
