{"type":"message","id":"0f4a14e9","parentId":"860f1c76","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:04:26.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API is returning HTML instead of JSON. This means the `/v1/crons` endpoint is actually serving the web UI, not a REST API. The earlier 200 status was misleading - it's just serving the HTML page for any unknown path.\n\nSo the gateway API doesn't have a REST endpoint for cron management that's accessible this way. The openclaw CLI must be using a different mechanism (maybe WebSocket or a different port) to communicate with the gateway.\n\nThis explains why the CLI is hanging - it's trying to connect via a specific channel that's not working.\n\nOK, so I can't manage crons via HTTP API. Let me try a different approach.\n\nThe core problem is: the QLHV cron is stuck in a loop because it can't send to the ended group session. \n\nThe simplest fix is to send a new message to the group to restart its session, which would let the cron succeed. Alternatively, I could bypass the cron entirely and handle the reporting differently - maybe having the master-orchestrator send the report directly on a timer instead of relying on the stuck cron. The real issue is that the cron is stuck trying to reach a session that's no longer active.\n\nSince the group session ended, the cron keeps failing and the gateway auto-restarts it, creating that timeout loop. The cleanest solution is to delete the cron and set up a new one with a fresh session. But since the CLI is hanging, I should try a different approach - maybe using the `expect` tool or running the openclaw command in a way that prevents it from hanging.\n\nActually, I could pipe input to the openclaw CLI to sidestep the interactive timeout. Or better yet, I could send a task to the master-orchestrator to delete and recreate the cron using the API directly. Let me check the internal API endpoints that were showing 200 responses earlier.","thinkingSignature":"0786e20002232518f62866c27b4617701503e2ce13a649760aad539dd51a97c8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uprplz6xpuu8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"83eaaf256ae54e4fa1bf7798033cfe591438bcdff21417b3\"\ncurl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" http://127.0.0.1:18789/internal/crons 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":405,"output":472,"cacheRead":42070,"cacheWrite":647,"totalTokens":43594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056655028,"responseId":"062bac5026411c912e9db42ce06dedcb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc584e74","parentId":"0f4a14e9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:04:27.281Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uprplz6xpuu8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>OpenClaw Control</title>\n    <meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"dark light\" />\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"./favicon.svg\" />\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"./favicon-32.png\" />\n    <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"./apple-touch-icon.png\" />\n    <script>\n      (function () {\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n        var MODES = { system: 1, light: 1, dark: 1 };\n        var LEGACY = {\n          dark: \"claw:dark\",\n          light: \"claw:light\",\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n          fieldmanual: \"dash:dark\",\n          clawdash: \"dash:light\",\n          system: \"claw:system\",\n        };\n        try {\n          var keys = Object.keys(localStorage);\n          var raw;\n          for (var i = 0; i < keys.length; i++) {\n            if (keys[i].indexOf(\"openclaw.control.settings.v1\") === 0) {\n              raw = localStorage.getItem(keys[i]);\n              if (raw) break;\n            }\n          }\n          if (!raw) return;\n          var s = JSON.parse(raw);\n          var t = s && s.theme;\n          var m = s && s.themeMode;\n          if (typeof t !== \"string\") t = \"\";\n          if (typeof m !== \"string\") m = \"\";\n          var legacy = LEGACY[t];\n          var theme = THEMES[t] ? t : legacy ? legacy.split(\":\")[0] : \"claw\";\n          var mode = MODES[m] ? m : legacy ? legacy.split(\":\")[1] : \"system\";\n          if (mode === \"system\") {\n            mode = window.matchMedia(\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\").matches ? \"light\" : \"dark\";\n          }\n          var resolved =\n            theme === \"knot\"\n              ? mode === \"light\"\n                ? \"openknot-light\"\n                : \"openknot\"\n              : theme === \"dash\"\n                ? mode === \"light\"\n                  ? \"dash-light\"\n                  : \"dash\"\n                : mode === \"light\"\n                  ? \"light\"\n                  : \"dark\";\n          document.documentElement.setAttribute(\"data-theme\", resolved);\n          document.documentElement.setAttribute(\n            \"data-theme-mode\",\n            resolved.indexOf(\"light\") !== -1 ? \"light\" : \"dark\",\n          );\n        } catch (e) {}\n      })();\n    </script>\n    <script type=\"module\" crossorigin src=\"./assets/index-Dts6VHgr.js\"></script>\n    <link rel=\"modulepreload\" crossorigin href=\"./assets/i18n-BTxWaFnv.js\">\n    <link rel=\"modulepreload\" crossorigin href=\"./assets/directive-Dk4hInuL.js\">\n    <link rel=\"modulepreload\" crossorigin href=\"./assets/format-1xo3usjI.js\">\n    <link rel=\"modulepreload\" crossorigin href=\"./assets/string-coerce-BcFtIWA_.js\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" crossorigin href=\"./assets/index-BVXsoScG.css\">\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <openclaw-app></openclaw-app>\n  </body>\n</html>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":157,"aggregated":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>OpenClaw Control</title>\n    <meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"dark light\" />\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"./favicon.svg\" />\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"./favicon-32.png\" />\n    <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"./apple-touch-icon.png\" />\n    <script>\n      (function () {\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n        var MODES = { system: 1, light: 1, dark: 1 };\n        var LEGACY = {\n          dark: \"claw:dark\",\n          light: \"claw:light\",\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n          fieldmanual: \"dash:dark\",\n          clawdash: \"dash:light\",\n          system: \"claw:system\",\n        };\n        try {\n          var keys = Object.keys(localStorage);\n          var raw;\n          for (var i = 0; i < keys.length; i++) {\n            if (keys[i].indexOf(\"openclaw.control.settings.v1\") === 0) {\n              raw = localStorage.getItem(keys[i]);\n              if (raw) break;\n            }\n          }\n          if (!raw) return;\n          var s = JSON.parse(raw);\n          var t = s && s.theme;\n          var m = s && s.themeMode;\n          if (typeof t !== \"string\") t = \"\";\n          if (typeof m !== \"string\") m = \"\";\n          var legacy = LEGACY[t];\n          var theme = THEMES[t] ? t : legacy ? legacy.split(\":\")[0] : \"claw\";\n          var mode = MODES[m] ? m : legacy ? legacy.split(\":\")[1] : \"system\";\n          if (mode === \"system\") {\n            mode = window.matchMedia(\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\").matches ? \"light\" : \"dark\";\n          }\n          var resolved =\n            theme === \"knot\"\n              ? mode === \"light\"\n                ? \"openknot-light\"\n                : \"openknot\"\n              : theme === \"dash\"\n                ? mode === \"light\"\n                  ? \"dash-light\"\n                  : \"dash\"\n                : mode === \"light\"\n                  ? \"light\"\n                  : \"dark\";\n          document.documentElement.setAttribute(\"data-theme\", resolved);\n          document.documentElement.setAttribute(\n            \"data-theme-mode\",\n            resolved.indexOf(\"light\") !== -1 ? \"light\" : \"dark\",\n          );\n        } catch (e) {}\n      })();\n    </script>\n    <script type=\"module\" crossorigin src=\"./assets/index-Dts6VHgr.js\"></script>