{"type":"message","id":"c71c27bf","parentId":"58ecb314","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:08:11.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see:1. `ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7.jsonl` - 128304 bytes! This is the QLHV cron, and it's HUGE (128KB). This confirms it's been running a lot and generating a lot of content. It's still in the runs directory, which means it's NOT in the jobs.json but the gateway is still running it somehow.2. `6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31.jsonl` - 94937 bytes - This is the DTLX cron. It's been running and generating content.3. \n\nThe other cron files are tiny in comparison. The QLHV cron is taking up 128KB, which is a red flag that something's off. The file is still being written to, which means the cron is actively running, but it's not registered in jobs.json—so either it's a legacy entry or something else is managing it. Let me look at what's actually in that file to figure out what's going on.","thinkingSignature":"d8701320664470860077760c54afa6ce21faf9c7a3f78e8b484664f363111bca"},{"type":"text","text":"QLHV cron file lớn bất thường (128KB)! Để xem nó đang làm gì:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bv1rnhz6cgar_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -5 /root/.openclaw/cron/runs/ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7.jsonl | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    line = line.strip()\n    if not line: continue\n    try:\n        obj = json.loads(line)\n        role = obj.get('role', '?')\n        ts = obj.get('timestamp', '?')\n        sr = obj.get('stopReason', obj.get('errorMessage', '?'))\n        content = obj.get('content', '')\n        if isinstance(content, list):\n            for c in content:\n                if isinstance(c, dict) and c.get('type') == 'text':\n                    content = c.get('text', '')[:200]\n                    break\n        print(f'[{ts}] {role} | stopReason: {str(sr)[:50]} | content: {str(content)[:100]}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'Parse error: {e} | {line[:100]}')\n\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1008,"output":517,"cacheRead":50804,"cacheWrite":3466,"totalTokens":55795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056878954,"responseId":"062bad30ab83fb1a1f487e8777a28616"}}
